headline: Q1 2026 Insurance Labor Market Study Results to be Highlighted in Webinar
summary: CHICAGO, February 03, 2026--The results of the Q1 2026 U.S. Insurance Labor Market Study will be revealed in a webinar presentation at 1 p.m. CT on February 19, 2026.
